## Skill Manager

I can help you manage Russell skills:

### Commands

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `russell skill list` | List installed skills |
| `russell skill stats` | Show skill telemetry |
| `russell skill check <id>` | Validate a skill manifest |
| `russell skill build <id>` | Create new skill skeleton |
| `russell skill install <id>` | Install a skill |
| `russell skill prune <id>` | Temporarily disable |
| `russell skill restore <id>` | Re-enable pruned skill |
| `russell skill retire <id>` | Archive and remove |
| `russell skill rebuild-cache` | Refresh symptom mappings |

